Installing on Linux systems.
----------------------------

- Notice that g++ with c++11 is available on compilers up to 4.7.6 versions.
- Boost also is need on versions 1.48 or greater.
- Libpcap 0.8 
- Log4cxx is optional

./configure
make 
make install

Installing on BSD systems.
--------------------------

./configure
make -i

BSD versions can not compile the python binding due to a limitation on the compilation system.

